SERVERALERT:
<html><body>
<h1 align="left">21st February 2021</h1>
<p>A big update was recently pushed to the closed alpha test realm. Release notes are in <a href="https://discord.gg/Sag44ar">Discord</a>.<br/><br/></p>
<h1 align="left">9th December 2020</h1>
<p>A lot of major updates have been pushed to the live realm for the weekend open alpha test. Please report any issues or feedback through our <a href="https://discord.gg/Sag44ar">Discord</a>.<br/><br/></p>
<h1 align="left">21st November 2020</h1>
<p>The World's End dungeon is now playable. This update also includes a lot of minor fixes and updates.<br/><br/></p>
<h1 align="left">11th November 2020</h1>
<p>The Stormwind Vault solo dungeon is now playable.<br/><br/></p>
<h1 align="left">1st October 2020</h1>
<p>Welcome to another Hour of Twilight alpha test. This is still a very early stage test, so please keep in mind that some things will be broken or unbalanced. Please report any constructive feedback through our <a href="https://discord.gg/Sag44ar">Discord</a>.<br/><br/></p>
<p>The Adventurer class is now the only playable class.<br/><br/></p>
<p>The Pirate Seas dungeon has been removed. It was a fun idea but in reality transports are too buggy.<br/><br/></p>
<p>All information on the server can be accessed through our <a href="https://discord.gg/Sag44ar">Discord</a>.<br/><br/></p>
<p>Have fun.<br/><br/></p>
<h1 align="left">19th July 2020</h1>
<p>Welcome to the Hour of Twilight alpha. Please keep in mind that:<br/><br/></p>
<p>Expect things to be broken. This is still a very early stage alpha, when you find broken or unbalanced content please report the issues through our Discord.<br/><br/></p>
<p>The Adventurer class is not playable. You can create one however you will not have any abilities.<br/><br/></p>
<p>To create an account please join our <a href="https://discord.gg/Sag44ar">Discord</a>.<br/><br/></p>
<p>We hope you have fun and enjoy the server.<br/><br/></p>
</body></html>
